# Title: TeamViewer Log File Deleted
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-01-16
# Level: low
# Description: Detects the deletion of the TeamViewer log files which may indicate an attempt to destroy forensic evidence
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_delete/file_delete_win_delete_teamviewer_logs.yml

TargetFilename="*\\TeamViewer_*" TargetFilename="*.log" NOT Image="C:\\Windows\\system32\\svchost.exe"